{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/dwango-cosplay-agency-agensi-untuk-pekerjaan-berbasis-cosplaying/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Dwango “Cosplay Agency”: Agensi Untuk Pekerjaan Berbasis Cosplaying","content":"<p>Pada awal kelahiran dan masa perintisannya di pop culture dunia, “Cosplay” adalah sebuah hobby dan “Cosplayer” bukanlah sebuah profesi untuk bisnis.</p>\n<p>Cosplay adalah perwujudan <em>passion</em> akan satu karakter imajinasi ke dalam bentuk nyata. Perwujudannya ada di bagian penampilan (<em>hairdo, make up, costume</em>) serta karakteristik saat berpenampilan seperti karakter yang di-cosplay-kan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46507\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46507\" data-attachment-id=\"46507\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Karakter 2B oleh Cosplayer Sherry Dayo. (Sumber: Facebook SherryCosplayer)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Karakter 2B oleh Cosplayer Sherry Dayo. (Sumber: Facebook SherryCosplayer)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46507\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2.jpg\" alt=\"Karakter 2B oleh Cosplayer Sherry Dayo. (Sumber: Facebook SherryCosplayer)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46507\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Karakter 2B oleh Cosplayer Sherry Dayo. (Sumber: Facebook SherryCosplayer)</p></div></p>\n<p>Seorang <em>cosplayer</em> hampir semuanya lahir karena <em>passion</em> tadi. Karena rasa cinta. Dengan meniru penampilan dan karakteristik karakter yang dia sukai dalam format <em>cosplaying</em>, seorang fans akan menemukan kebahagiaan atau apapun yang dia ingin rasakan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46508\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46508\" data-attachment-id=\"46508\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Karakter Honoka Kosaka oleh Cosplayer Nina Yin Kazama. (Sumber: WorldCosplay)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Karakter Honoka Kosaka oleh Cosplayer Nina Yin Kazama. (Sumber: WorldCosplay)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46508\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3.jpg\" alt=\"Karakter Honoka Kosaka oleh Cosplayer Nina Yin Kazama. (Sumber: WorldCosplay)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46508\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Karakter Honoka Kosaka oleh Cosplayer Nina Yin Kazama. (Sumber: WorldCosplay)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi saat ini sudah terjadi pergeseran akan makna dan fungsi cosplay di berbagai tempat di dunia. Dengan semakin berkembangnya kemampuan seorang cosplayer dalam merakit dan mendesain kostum mereka (baik dengan bahan standard hingga premium) serta keahlian lain pendukung <em>cosplaying</em> (<em>styling wig,</em> <em>make up</em> dan lainnya), cosplayer mulai dilirik dengan serius oleh pihak-pihak yang berkepentingan; terutama oleh media dan perusahaan asal IP karakter yang di-cosplay-kan.</p>\n<p>Bukan untuk dilarang atau diganggu; tapi justru untuk digandeng. Karena sekarang semakin biasa dan normal untuk sebuah perusahaan menggunakan jasa seorang cosplayer untuk kepentingan bisnis. Promosi. Marketing purpose. Menjadi wajah perusahaan. Model produk. Contoh nyata dari kondisi ini misalnya ada pada cosplayer Jessica Nigri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46511\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46511\" data-attachment-id=\"46511\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer Jessica Nigri. (Sumber: YouTube)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer Jessica Nigri. (Sumber: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46511\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplayer Jessica Nigri. (Sumber: YouTube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46511\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer Jessica Nigri. (Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jessica Nigri, yang sekarang bisa dibilang sangat terkenal di cosplay scene dunia, awalnya juga merupakan <em>cosplayer hobbyist</em>. Kebiasaannya melakukan <em>cosplaying character</em> dengan pendekatan yang <em>-ahem-</em> lewd alias seksi membuat namanya cepat melambung ke papan atas. Dengan ditunjang proporsi tubuh yang baik, wajah menarik dan kepribadian lucu &amp; ramah (baik di internet maupun dunia nyata) membuat Jessica Nigri berubah haluan dari “cosplay untuk hiburan” menjadi “cosplay untuk bisnis”.</p>\n<p>Selain berjualan <em>merchandise</em> dirinya sendiri, Nigri juga dikenal di kalangan <em>publisher video games</em>. Dia bahkan sempat menjadi cosplayer resmi untuk <em>game</em> buatan desainer <em>game</em> terkenal Goichi Suda / Suda51 yang berjudul “Lollipop Chainsaw”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46510\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46510\" data-attachment-id=\"46510\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"James Gunn, Jessica Nigri &#038; Suda51. (Sumber: Pinterest)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;James Gunn, Jessica Nigri &#038; Suda51. (Sumber: Pinterest)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46510\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5.jpg\" alt=\"James Gunn, Jessica Nigri &amp; Suda51. (Sumber: Pinterest)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">James Gunn, Jessica Nigri &amp; Suda51. (Sumber: Pinterest)</p></div></p>\n<p>Ada pula <em>cosplayer</em> Australia asal Indonesia, Pinky Lu Xun, yang menjadi <em>cosplayer</em> resmi untuk karakter dari majalah komik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46513\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46513\" data-attachment-id=\"46513\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Karakter Lay Lay Cat oleh Cosplayer Pinky Lu Xun. (Sumber: Twitter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Karakter Lay Lay Cat oleh Cosplayer Pinky Lu Xun. (Sumber: Twitter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46513\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8.jpg\" alt=\"Karakter Lay Lay Cat oleh Cosplayer Pinky Lu Xun. (Sumber: Twitter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Karakter Lay Lay Cat oleh Cosplayer Pinky Lu Xun. (Sumber: Twitter)</p></div></p>\n<p>Cosplayer lainnya, Plant Lily dari Vietnam, memang belum mewakili sebuah karakter korporasi seperti Nigri maupun Pinky tapi dia juga sedang merintis jalan sebagai cosplayer professional seperti mereka. Tidak hanya cosplaying untuk hobby saja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46509\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46509\" data-attachment-id=\"46509\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer Plant Lily. (Sumber: CIAYO Blog)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer Plant Lily. (Sumber: CIAYO Blog)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46509\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplayer Plant Lily. (Sumber: CIAYO Blog)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46509\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer Plant Lily. (Sumber: CIAYO Blog)</p></div></p>\n<p>Para ‘<em>cosplayer talent</em>’ ini biasanya me-<em>manage</em> sendiri kegiatan bisnis cosplay mereka. Dwango, operator dari <em>website streaming</em> besar Jepang “Nico Nico Douga”, mencoba memberikan solusi professional dan internasional sebagai manajemen cosplayer untuk mereka yang sedang merintis karir <em>cosplaying</em> mereka secara serius. Kira-kira seperti sebuah ‘<em>modelling agency</em>’.</p>\n<p>Mereka menggunakan merk “<em>Cosplay Agency</em>” untuk perusahaan ini. Sebuah nama yang tidak basa-basi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46505\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46505\" data-attachment-id=\"46505\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/coasgen9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CosplayAgency\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CosplayAgency&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46505\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CosplayAgency\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coasgen9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46505\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CosplayAgency</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Cosplay Agency</em> dari Dwango ini menempatkan diri sebagai titik penghubung antara cosplayer dengan klien pengguna jasa cosplayer. Jadi hampir sama dengan sebuah agen <em>modelling</em> di dunia foto model / model <em>runway</em>. Setelah mendaftar di <em>Cosplay Agency</em>, seorang cosplayer akan mendapatkan halaman profil yang bisa diisi dengan foto-foto contoh beserta data profil lainnya agar calon klien bisa lihat dan pelajari lebih lanjut.</p>\n<p>Cosplayer juga dapat menampilkan ‘<em>extra points</em>’ mereka sebagai nilai jual, seperti misalnya kemampuan menyanyi, menari, akting, menjadi MC acara, dan hal-hal <em>entertainment-worthy</em> lain.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46512\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46512\" data-attachment-id=\"46512\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Isi dan lengkapi profil dengan sebaik-baiknya di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Isi dan lengkapi profil dengan sebaik-baiknya di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46512\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7.jpg\" alt=\"Isi dan lengkapi profil dengan sebaik-baiknya di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46512\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Isi dan lengkapi profil dengan sebaik-baiknya di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan menampilkan semua yang terbaik yang bisa ditawarkan (termasuk mungkin kemampuan bahasa asing atau kesediaan melakukan perjalanan ke luar negeri) akan memudahkan calon klien pengguna jasa cosplayer dalam menilai cocok tidaknya mereka menggunakan jasa cosplayer yang di-<em>manage</em> oleh Cosplay Agency dari Dwango ini.</p>\n<p>Karena walaupun berpusat dan beraktivitas di Jepang, Dwango<em> Cosplay Agency</em> sepertinya tidak menutup diri hanya untuk cosplayer negara Jepang. <em>Cosplayer</em> negara lain bisa mencoba untuk bergabung di manajemen <em>Cosplay Agency</em> ini. Walau saya pribadi menilai akan sulit untuk cosplayer di luar Jepang tampil menarik perhatian disana jika tampil biasa-biasa saja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46506\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46506\" data-attachment-id=\"46506\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/attachment/cosagen1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer non-Jepang di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer non-Jepang di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46506\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplayer non-Jepang di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cosagen1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46506\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer non-Jepang di Cosplay Agency. (Sumber: CosplayAgency)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi kalau Anda seorang cosplayer, percaya diri dengan <em>skill crafting costume</em>, dan punya keinginan menjadi seorang cosplayer internasional dan professional seperti mereka-mereka yang sudah berada di level itu, mengapa tidak mencoba diwakili oleh <a href=\"http://cosplayagency.jp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Cosplay Agency</em></a>?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"75f16da7-50ab-5b09-89d2-9def924b1d52"}}}